        public static org.eclipse.collections.api.list.ImmutableList<edu.kit.ipd.parse.luna.graph.INode> getINodesInOrder​(edu.kit.ipd.parse.luna.graph.IGraph graph)
        Returns the "main" INodes in order. This means that "token"-type INodes are collected and returned in a sorted list. Sorting is based on the "next"-arc, starting with the first utterance node.
        Parameters:
        graph - Graph representing an input
        Returns:
        Sorted List of "token"-INodes
